org.fishwife.jrugged.spring

Class PerformanceMonitorBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fishwife.jrugged.PerformanceMonitor
      • org.fishwife.jrugged.spring.PerformanceMonitorBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServiceWrapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PerformanceMonitorFilter

    @ManagedResource
public class PerformanceMonitorBean
extends PerformanceMonitor
    The PerformanceMonitorBean is a straightforward wrapper around a PerformanceMonitor that allows for leveraging automated exposure of the information via Spring's JMX annotations.
